IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DRIVER.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-PRINCIPAL    PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 10000.00.
01 WS-RATE         PIC 9(3)V9999 VALUE 4.5000.
01 WS-YEARS        PIC 9(2) VALUE 10.
01 WS-RESULT       PIC 9(9)V99.
01 WS-RETURN       PIC 9(4).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY 'Before call'
    CALL 'CALCINTEREST' USING WS-PRINCIPAL WS-RATE
                              WS-YEARS WS-RESULT
    MOVE RETURN-CODE TO WS-RETURN
    DISPLAY 'After call, return code: ' WS-RETURN
    DISPLAY 'Result: ' WS-RESULT
    STOP RUN.